{"tid":592272,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"球壇預言：摩二季發功 曼聯後上封王","createTime":"2018-03-14T05:37:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T09:57:22.000Z","uid":57035,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"399da3109bdadc677727d612ae1678b6f4a933b5","tid":592272,"uid":57035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T05:37:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20171231/photo/bkn-20171231053015614-1231_00882_001_01p.jpg?20171231053346\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20171231%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171231053015614-1231_00882_001_01p.jpg%3F20171231053346&h=a08cbb38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然今季英超爭標形勢，「1哥」曼城已經甩開同市死敵曼聯15分，但千祈唔好忘記，紅魔主帥莫連奴每逢執教球隊第2季例必有貨交，以往佢執教波圖、車路士、皇家馬德里同國際米蘭，第2季都一定有聯賽冠軍落袋，而且聯賽仲有半季未踢，咁快就斷定曼城捧盃又言之尚早。<br />\n<br />\n果然，「藍月亮」喺下半季出現嚴重傷兵潮，兩大射手阿古路及加比爾西捷西斯又因爭位踢搞到不和，軍心不穩令曼聯有機可乘，季尾以1分之微反壓死敵，第14次稱霸英超，重演95-96年度球季，費格遜麾下嘅紅魔喺1月一度落後紐卡素12分下大逆轉奪冠，「莫二季」真係堅過石堅。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20171231/bkn-20171231053015614-1231_00882_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fsport%2F20171231%2Fbkn-20171231053015614-1231_00882_001.html&d=YFFXd4KYqv50WCakF7OTpk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=9c3e9346\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/sport/20171231/bkn-20171231053015614-1231_00882_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9b97eac5b389d5e81acad7c8c156e17472d61e67","tid":592272,"uid":14652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T05:38:20.000Z","msg":"好撚堅呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"010a8677f2dd3870be2be1ba558889b654e49396","tid":592272,"uid":46608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T05:39:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets